column: future
---
body:
Further AI-assisted automation: linking metadata to authoritative identifiers
(authors to ORCID, affiliations and funders to ROR), deriving metadata from
record context (e.g. subject classification from abstracts), and reviewing
records against repository and community curation policies.
---
category: Projects
---
title: AIRDEC: Advanced AI-assisted metadata and curation
---
year: 2026
